sourcesContent: import React, { Component } from "react"; import { Card, CardBody, CardHeader, Label, Input, FormGroup, CardFooter, Button, Col } from 'reactstrap'; const initialValues = { realmId: '', realmCountryId: '', organisationId: '', programManagerUserId: '', airFreightPercentage: '', seaFreightPercentage: '', deliveredToRecivedLeadTime: '', draftToSubmittedLeadTime: '', planDraftLeadTime: '', submittedToApprovedLeadTime: '', approvedToShippedLeadTime: '', monthInFutureForAmc: '', monthInPastForAmc: '', healthAreaId: '', programNotes: '' } const validationSchema = function (values) { return Yup.object().shape({ realmId: Yup.string() .required("Please select realm"), realmCountryId: Yup.string() .required('Please select country.'), organisationId: Yup.string() .required('Please select organisation'), programManagerUserId: Yup.string() .required('Please select program manager'), airFreightPercentage: Yup.string() .required('Please enter air freight percentage'), seaFreightPercentage: Yup.string() .required('Please enter sea freight percentage'), deliveredToRecivedLeadTime: Yup.string() .required('Please enter deliverd to recived lead time'), draftToSubmittedLeadTime: Yup.string() .required('Please enter draft to submitted lead time'), planDraftLeadTime: Yup.string() .required('Please enter plan to draft lead time'), submittedToApprovedLeadTime: Yup.string() .required('Please enter submit to approved lead time'), approvedToShippedLeadTime: Yup.string() .required('Please enter approved to shippedLeadTime'), monthInFutureForAmc: Yup.string() .required('Please enter month in funture for AMC'), healthAreaId: Yup.string() .required('Please enter month in past fro AMC'), programNotes: Yup.string() .required('Please enter notes'), }) } const validate = (getValidationSchema) => { return (values) => { const validationSchema = getValidationSchema(values) try { validationSchema.validateSync(values, { abortEarly: false }) return {} } catch (error) { return getErrorsFromValidationError(error) } } } const getErrorsFromValidationError = (validationError) => { const FIRST_ERROR = 0 return validationError.inner.reduce((errors, error) => { return { ...errors, [error.path]: error.errors[FIRST_ERROR], } }, {}) } export default class AddProgram extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { program: { label: { label_en: '' }, realm: { realmId: '' }, realmCountry: { realmCountryId: '' }, organisation: { organisationId: '' }, programManager: { programManagerUserId: '' }, airFreightPercentage: '', seaFreightPercentage: '', deliveredToRecivedLeadTime: '', draftToSubmittedLeadTime: '', planDraftLeadTime: '', submittedToApprovedLeadTime: '', approvedToShippedLeadTime: '', monthInFutureForAmc: '', monthInPastForAmc: '', healthAreaId: '', programNotes: '' } } this.dataChange = this.dataChange.bind(this); } dataChange(event) { } render() { return ( Add Program ); } }
